entry.title: Assam Police Recruitment 2022 Soon for 5200 Constable, SI Vacancy
entry.summary: The Assam government will soon Recruit 12,000 posts including 5,200 constables and sub-inspectors in the Home Department, This was announced by Chief Minister Himanta Biswa Sarma. Online applications are invited by the State Level Police Recruitment Board, Assam for recruitment to the posts of Constable, Sub Inspector.
